(211, 3, 'http://rss.cnn.com/~r/rss/cnn_world/~3/GVxNwLC2q7w/index.html', '2013-09-06 16:39:29', 'Writer who fled Taliban gunned down', 'writer,fled,taliban,gunned,down', 'An Indian author whose memoir about her dramatic escape from the Taliban became a Bollywood movie was shot dead by militants in Afghanistan, police said Thursday.\n    \n', 'indian,author,whose,memoir,about,dramatic,escape,from,taliban,became,bollywood,movie,shot,dead,militants,afghanistan,police,said,thursday', '', 'writer,fled,taliban,gunned,down,indian,author,whose,memoir,about,dramatic,escape,from,became,bollywood,movie,shot,dead,militants,afghanistan,police,said,thursday', NULL, '2013-09-07 07:54:40'),
