(215, 3, 'http://rss.cnn.com/~r/rss/cnn_world/~3/GB9T8MbrpYg/index.html', '2013-09-05 15:11:04', 'Report: Vigilante targeting Mexican bus drivers', 'report,vigilante,targeting,mexican,drivers', 'She calls herself &quot;Diana, the Hunter.&quot; Authorities say the elusive woman has killed at least two bus drivers in Ciudad Juarez, Mexico. Media report that they have received e-mails from the suspect, claiming the killings were to avenge women who have been raped by bus drivers.\n    \n', 'calls,herself,diana,hunter,authorities,elusive,woman,killed,least,drivers,ciudad,juarez,mexico,media,report,that,they,have,received,mails,from,suspect,claiming,killings,were,avenge,women,been,raped', '', 'report,vigilante,targeting,mexican,drivers,calls,herself,diana,hunter,authorities,elusive,woman,killed,least,ciudad,juarez,mexico,media,that,they,have,received,mails,from,suspect,claiming,killings,were,avenge,women,been,raped', NULL, '2013-09-07 07:54:40'),
