(220, 3, 'http://rss.cnn.com/~r/rss/cnn_world/~3/A19oudMRBeY/index.html', '2013-09-05 17:01:43', 'Reports: U.S. spied on Brazil, Mexico', 'reports,spied,brazil,mexico', 'Brazil and Mexico summoned U.S. ambassadors Monday after media reports that the United States had spied on their countries&#039; presidents.\n    \n', 'brazil,mexico,summoned,ambassadors,monday,after,media,reports,that,united,states,spied,their,countries,presidents', '', 'reports,spied,brazil,mexico,summoned,ambassadors,monday,after,media,that,united,states,their,countries,presidents', NULL, '2013-09-07 07:54:40'),
