(245, 4, 'http://feeds.washingtonpost.com/c/34656/f/636708/s/30d547da/sc/8/l/0L0Swashingtonpost0N0Cworld0Cin0Erussia0Ea0Eparallel0Eg0E20A0Efor0Eyoung0Ewomen0C20A130C0A90C0A40C9f0A3212a0E14aa0E11e30Eb220A0E2c950Ac7f32630Istory0Bhtml0Dwprss0Frss0Iworld/story01.htm', '2013-09-05 14:46:46', 'In Russia, a parallel G-20 for young women', 'russia,parallel,young,women', 'MOSCOW &mdash; A group of young women want to send a message to the mostly male leaders of the Group of 20 nations meeting in St. Petersburg this week: Don&rsquo;t forget us. Over the summer, young women from the G-20 countries, plus one each from the European Union and African Union, met in Moscow for a gathering sponsored by G(irls)20 Summit, a Canadian-based organization that has been holding similar meetings every year since 2010.  Read full article &amp;#62;&amp;#62;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;', 'moscow,group,young,women,want,send,message,mostly,male,leaders,nations,meeting,petersburg,this,week,forget,over,summer,from,countries,plus,each,european,union,african,gathering,sponsored,irls,summit,canadian,based,organization,that,been,holding,similar,meetings,every,year,since,2010,read,full,article,nbsp', '', 'russia,parallel,young,women,moscow,group,want,send,message,mostly,male,leaders,nations,meeting,petersburg,this,week,forget,over,summer,from,countries,plus,each,european,union,african,gathering,sponsored,irls,summit,canadian,based,organization,that,been,holding,similar,meetings,every,year,since,2010,read,full,article,nbsp', NULL, '2013-09-07 07:54:42');
